8:["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg","children":"The tone is deliberate: premium, strategic, intelligent, mature, connected, trustworthy, architected. Nothing about the system should read as hustle culture, startup theater, or generic solar marketing."}],["$","blockquote",null,{"className":"border-l-2 border-accent pl-6 italic text-foreground","children":"C² operates as the root intelligence behind a connected ecosystem. It gives shape to effort, clarity to energy, and continuity to every deal that returns value to the whole."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground","children":"Operating Principles"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-text-primary","children":"Distinct branches:"}]," each audience gets a page built for their role, not a watered-down generic message."]}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-text-primary","children":"Shared standards:"}]," design, language, and trust signals stay connected across the family."]}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-text-primary","children":"Measured pathways:"}]," movement between branches is clear, but never forced or salesy."]}]]}],["$","li",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-text-primary","children":"Reputation compounding:"}]," public education, partner growth, and build quality reinforce one another."]}]]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground","children":"The Cyclical System"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The operating idea is cyclical. Effort becomes energy. Energy becomes deals. Deals return as energy. The result is a self-sustaining system in which public trust, partner growth, and field execution are designed to reinforce each other rather than compete for attention."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-text-tertiary","children":"This document is a living standard. It evolves as the ecosystem evolves, but its foundational tone — premium, strategic, architected — is permanent."}]]}]
